<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 12:13:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国际奥斯维辛委员会要求“立即无条件”释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/international-auschwitz-council-demands-immediate-and-unconditional-release-of-hostages/0000018b-ec5e-d36e-a3cb-fc5fe9d40000</link><description>国际奥斯维辛委员会对以色列表示“坚定不移的声援”，并呼吁“立即无条件释放”人质，以此作为“制止可怕的死亡螺旋的重要第一步”</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 11:41:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/international-auschwitz-council-demands-immediate-and-unconditional-release-of-hostages/0000018b-ec5e-d36e-a3cb-fc5fe9d40000</guid></item><item><title>“谈论生命，而不是死亡”：以色列人质家属恳求政府放弃恐怖分子死刑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/talk-life-not-death-israeli-hostage-families-beg-govt-to-drop-terrorist-death-penalty/0000018b-ec3c-d6b8-a5ab-ec7e96300000</link><description>尽管哈马斯战争期间在加沙被扣为人质的人的家人含泪恳求，内塔尼亚胡的极右翼伙伴仍坚持举行法律辩论</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 10:41:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/talk-life-not-death-israeli-hostage-families-beg-govt-to-drop-terrorist-death-penalty/0000018b-ec3c-d6b8-a5ab-ec7e96300000</guid></item><item><title>我们班有 13 个基布兹孩子。我们无法想象这次恐怖袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-were-a-class-of-13-kibbutz-kids-we-never-could-imagine-this-would-happen/0000018b-e7ca-d05f-a5eb-e7ea55580000</link><description>哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击的后果：我们出生于 1972 年，在后来被哈马斯摧毁的基布兹共同生活后就分道扬镳了。我们每个人都被尚未结束的暴行所摧毁</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 10:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-were-a-class-of-13-kibbutz-kids-we-never-could-imagine-this-would-happen/0000018b-e7ca-d05f-a5eb-e7ea55580000</guid></item><item><title>随着反犹太主义的加剧，英国犹太人询问他们在英国是否有未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/with-antisemitism-spiking-uk-jews-ask-if-they-have-a-future-in-britain/0000018b-e7a1-d963-a1bb-f7fbede00000</link><description>在英国，我们面临着世界上最糟糕的情况：伊斯兰极端主义反犹太主义与对美国批判种族理论和后殖民罪恶感的简单化解释相结合。自哈马斯发动袭击以来，犹太人仇恨情绪高涨 — — 并且缺乏盟友</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 09:51:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/with-antisemitism-spiking-uk-jews-ask-if-they-have-a-future-in-britain/0000018b-e7a1-d963-a1bb-f7fbede00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反对党提议修改民族国家法，增加“平等条款”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-opposition-party-proposes-amending-nation-state-law-with-equality-clause/0000018b-ebbf-d6b8-a5ab-efffca0a0000</link><description>虽然利库德集团尚未表示是否愿意支持一项修正案，但它已提出了一项关于德鲁兹人的基本法，可能是为了阻止这样的修正案，因为德鲁兹人士兵在战斗中的死亡再次引发了关于准“德鲁兹人”的争论。民族国家宪法法</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 09:47:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/israeli-opposition-party-proposes-amending-nation-state-law-with-equality-clause/0000018b-ebbf-d6b8-a5ab-efffca0a0000</guid></item><item><title>25 年前，加沙国际机场开业。随后发生了第二次起义</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/25-years-ago-gaza-intl-airport-opened-then-came-the-second-intifada/0000018b-e6fd-dffa-adef-e6fd35a10000</link><description>美国总统首次登陆加沙，巴勒斯坦国家航空公司飞往中东各国首都，加沙人开始梦想独立。但随后爆发了战斗，该场被轰炸，此后被洗劫并拆除</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 07:31:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-20/ty-article-magazine/.premium/25-years-ago-gaza-intl-airport-opened-then-came-the-second-intifada/0000018b-e6fd-dffa-adef-e6fd35a10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队在加沙击毙三名哈马斯指挥官； 40辆救援卡车将进入拉斯维加斯大道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-live/idf-shows-footage-of-hostages-inside-al-shifa-says-soldier-was-taken-there-and-killed/0000018b-eb5e-d32d-abdb-ef5fb0370000</link><description>哈马斯扣押的人质家属恳求政府不要立法对恐怖分子判处死刑 ■ 以色列国防军公布在加沙地带被杀的两名以色列伞兵旅士兵的姓名 ■ 以色列安全内阁批准燃料进入加沙 ■ 哈马斯管理的加沙卫生部：以色列士兵包围印度尼西亚医院 ■ 卡塔尔总理称人质协议面临的挑战“非常小” ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵被杀； 236 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：12,300 人死亡</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 06:34:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article-live/idf-shows-footage-of-hostages-inside-al-shifa-says-soldier-was-taken-there-and-killed/0000018b-eb5e-d32d-abdb-ef5fb0370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列认为哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔不理智，使人质交易变得更加紧迫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/yemens-houthis-are-taking-aim-at-israel-for-iran/0000018b-e962-d6b8-a5ab-ed6a298a0000</link><description>尽管加沙地带北部仍然存在军事目标，但以色列需要权衡持续地面进攻的好处。 ■ 美国对与伊朗直接对抗持谨慎态度，但胡塞武装袭击的增加可能会迫使其采取行动</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 04:14:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/yemens-houthis-are-taking-aim-at-israel-for-iran/0000018b-e962-d6b8-a5ab-ed6a298a0000</guid></item><item><title>许多以色列人和巴勒斯坦人已经“清醒过来”。我拒绝做同样的事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/many-israelis-and-palestinians-have-sobered-up-i-refuse-to-do-the-same/0000018b-e90b-d32d-abdb-ef4bbc910000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 02:51:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-20/ty-article-opinion/.premium/many-israelis-and-palestinians-have-sobered-up-i-refuse-to-do-the-same/0000018b-e90b-d32d-abdb-ef4bbc910000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陆军研究：自地面入侵开始以来加沙火箭袭击次数减少</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/army-study-rocket-attacks-down-since-start-of-ground-invasion/0000018b-e939-d32d-abdb-ef7b70b00000</link><description>这一下降之所以引人注目，是因为与之前在加沙地带的行动相比，在当前的战斗中，以色列国防军并未优先考虑定位火箭弹或阻止袭击</description><pubDate>Mon, 20 Nov 2023 02:48:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-20/ty-article/.premium/army-study-rocket-attacks-down-since-start-of-ground-invasion/0000018b-e939-d32d-abdb-ef7b70b00000</guid></item><item><title>“另一种恐惧”：10 月 7 日之后阿拉伯人和犹太人共存的脆弱性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-19/ty-article/.highlight/a-different-kind-of-fear-the-fragility-of-arab-jewish-coexistence-after-october-7/0000018b-e8a3-d32d-abdb-eee3db6e0000</link><description>加沙战争已经过去六周了，对 2021 年 5 月犹太和阿拉伯公民之间骚乱的报复并未实现。这片黑暗中唯一的一丝善意的背后是什么？</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 21:21:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-19/ty-article/.highlight/a-different-kind-of-fear-the-fragility-of-arab-jewish-coexistence-after-october-7/0000018b-e8a3-d32d-abdb-eee3db6e0000</guid></item><item><title>纽约市长指责教授在城市校园里营造了针对犹太人的仇恨氛围</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/new-york-mayor-blames-professors-for-hateful-atmosphere-against-jews-on-city-campuses/0000018b-e94b-d36e-a3cb-f95f9e6c0000</link><description>市长埃里克·亚当斯 (Eric Adams) 在曼哈顿中央犹太教堂告诉会众，校园已“成为仇恨的避风港”</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 20:59:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/new-york-mayor-blames-professors-for-hateful-atmosphere-against-jews-on-city-campuses/0000018b-e94b-d36e-a3cb-f95f9e6c0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，以色列军队公布了加沙 Al-Shifa 医院内人质的录像</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/israeli-army-releases-footage-of-hostages-inside-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-on-oct-7/0000018b-e93d-d36e-a3cb-f97f56bb0000</link><description>此外，以色列军方发言人丹尼尔·哈加里表示，被绑架并带入加沙地带的士兵诺亚·马西亚诺先被带到希法医院附近的一处藏身公寓，随后又被带入医院，并在那里被谋杀。病理报告证实</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 20:29:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/israeli-army-releases-footage-of-hostages-inside-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-on-oct-7/0000018b-e93d-d36e-a3cb-f97f56bb0000</guid></item><item><title>将加沙交给多国部队是一个幻想</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/multinational-force-just-a-bypass-around-the-palestinian-authority/0000018b-e8ae-d6b8-a5ab-ecee5d580000</link><description>战争结束后，阿拉伯国家拒绝向加沙派遣军队，而内塔尼亚胡则排除了巴勒斯坦权力机构控制该地区的可能性。但由非阿拉伯多国部队掌权的想法毫无意义</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 20:06:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/multinational-force-just-a-bypass-around-the-palestinian-authority/0000018b-e8ae-d6b8-a5ab-ecee5d580000</guid></item><item><title>前以色列外交官呼吁建立国际联盟，其国民被哈马斯扣为人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/ex-israeli-diplomats-call-for-an-intl-coalition-whose-nationals-are-held-hostage-by-hamas/0000018b-e915-d36e-a3cb-f9571b900000</link><description>该组织的代表和以色列退休大使呼吁联合国任命一名人质问题特别代表，要求红十字会在与哈马斯打交道时更加自信</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 19:57:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/ex-israeli-diplomats-call-for-an-intl-coalition-whose-nationals-are-held-hostage-by-hamas/0000018b-e915-d36e-a3cb-f9571b900000</guid></item><item><title>美国相信内塔尼亚胡最终将支持控制加沙的巴勒斯坦权力机构</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-believes-netanyahu-will-eventually-support-palestinian-authority-controlling-gaza/0000018b-e88a-d6b8-a5ab-ecea67b10000</link><description>美国官员认为，如果巴勒斯坦权力机构同意停止在国际机构中针对以色列的行动，并结束其在以色列监狱中为被定罪的杀人犯提供极具争议的支付制度，耶路撒冷对巴勒斯坦权力机构的态度将会软化。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 19:22:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-believes-netanyahu-will-eventually-support-palestinian-authority-controlling-gaza/0000018b-e88a-d6b8-a5ab-ecea67b10000</guid></item><item><title>美国敦促以色列推迟对加沙南部的袭击，直到北部流离失所的巴勒斯坦人得到解决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-presses-to-delay-south-gaza-strikes-until-displaced-palestinians-are-accounted-for/0000018b-e8bd-d6b8-a5ab-ecfff6b10000</link><description>国家安全顾问乔恩·费纳表示，人们“真正担心”以色列将行动转移到南部，在以色列的敦促下，那里有数十万人逃离</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 19:09:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/u-s-presses-to-delay-south-gaza-strikes-until-displaced-palestinians-are-accounted-for/0000018b-e8bd-d6b8-a5ab-ecfff6b10000</guid></item><item><title>史前澳大利亚人将野狗与家人一起埋葬在空中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-19/ty-article/prehistoric-australians-buried-their-dingoes-in-the-sky-with-people/0000018b-e82d-d570-a7cf-fa7d9be60000</link><description>澳大利亚原住民终生饲养野狗，可能是几代人，这与该岛殖民时代野生小狗袭击的报道形成鲜明对比</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 16:25:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-19/ty-article/prehistoric-australians-buried-their-dingoes-in-the-sky-with-people/0000018b-e82d-d570-a7cf-fa7d9be60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的福音派恋情无助于削弱美国对以色列的支持</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/young-americans-dont-support-israel-netanyahus-affair-with-evangelicals-isnt-helping/0000018b-e7c1-d05f-a5eb-e7e15af30000</link><description>随着年轻的美国选民越来越倾向于支持巴勒斯坦人而不是以色列，一个团体仍然坚定地支持犹太国家 — — 这只会加剧以色列和民主党之间的分裂</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 16:02:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/young-americans-dont-support-israel-netanyahus-affair-with-evangelicals-isnt-helping/0000018b-e7c1-d05f-a5eb-e7e15af30000</guid></item><item><title>加拿大性侵犯中心主任因质疑哈马斯强奸以色列妇女的说法而被解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/americas/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/head-of-canadian-sexual-assault-center-fired-for-questioning-accounts-of-hamas-rapes/0000018b-e7f8-d05f-a5eb-e7f8d6c80000</link><description>阿尔伯塔大学性侵犯中心主任萨曼莎·皮尔森签署了一封信，提到“反复且未经证实的指控巴勒斯坦人犯有性暴力罪”</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 15:25:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/americas/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/head-of-canadian-sexual-assault-center-fired-for-questioning-accounts-of-hamas-rapes/0000018b-e7f8-d05f-a5eb-e7f8d6c80000</guid></item></channel></rss>